{"title":"06_Hexo-elemecdn加速Butterfly第三方js","slug":"Hexo/06_Hexo-elemecdn加速Butterfly第三方js","date":"2022-10-28T10:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-10-29T10:00:01.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo/06_Hexo-elemecdn加速Butterfly第三方js.json","excerpt":"摘要：Element","covers":["https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028222132106.png","https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221029143047143.png","https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028223148954.png","https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028223928594.png"],"content":"<p>摘要：Element<span id=\"more\"></span></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"前言\">前言</h1>\n<p>博客异常加载，f12发现 <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js\">https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js</a> （主因）和 <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/@fancyapps/ui/dist/fancybox.umd.js\">https://unpkg.com/@fancyapps/ui/dist/fancybox.umd.js</a> 报 520（520，当源站服务器向 <a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/CDN/420951?fromModule=lemma_inlink\">CDN</a> 返回空白、未知或意外响应时，会发生 520 错误），日常都返的 200</p>\n<p>基于此有了换 cdn 的想法。<a href=\"https://butterfly.js.org/posts/ceeb73f/#CDN\">butterfly 官方教程</a> 介绍了 local/jsdelivr/unpkg/cdnjs/custom 这些选择，都不是想要的，看到别人用的 Element cdn，学习一下</p>\n<h1 id=\"步骤\">步骤</h1>\n<p>参考文章：<a href=\"https://butterfly.js.org/posts/ceeb73f/#CDN\">butterfly官方教程#CDN</a>、<a href=\"https://anzhiy.cn/posts/fe76.html\">安知鱼 - 可用cdn整理</a>、<a href=\"https://blog.zhheo.com/p/790087d9.html#%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\">张洪 Heo - Butterfly CDN链接更改指南</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>修改源码</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>修改 themes/butterfly/scripts/events/cdn.js，新增 elemecdn 字段</p>\n<blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028222132106.png\" alt=\"image-20221028222132106\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">elemecdn</span>: <span class=\"string\">`https://npm.elemecdn.com/<span class=\"subst\">$&#123;name&#125;</span><span class=\"subst\">$&#123;verType&#125;</span>/<span class=\"subst\">$&#123;file&#125;</span>`</span>,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改 _config.butterfly.yml，CDN.third_party_provider</p>\n<blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221029143047143.png\" alt=\"image-20221029143047143\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />\nf12 看了下 网络，替换后没异常\n<img src=\"https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028223148954.png\" alt=\"image-20221028223148954\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>根据 <a href=\"https://blog.zhheo.com/p/790087d9.html#%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\">张洪 Heo - Butterfly CDN链接更改指南</a> 按需替换 cdn链接（需注意变量名，比如butterfly v4.4.0 fontawesome 写成 fontawesomeV6 似乎才会生效）</p>\n<blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://image.cpen.top/image/image-20221028223928594.png\" alt=\"image-20221028223928594\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">CDN:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">option:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># 张洪Heo   https://blog.zhheo.com/p/790087d9.html</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># algolia_js: https://cdn1.tianli0.top/npm/js-heo@1.0.11/algolia/algolia.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># algolia_search: https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/instantsearch.js/2.10.5/instantsearch.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># algolia_search_css: https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/instantsearch.js/2.10.5/instantsearch.min.css</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">jquery:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">pjax:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lib.baomitu.com/pjax/0.2.8/pjax.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">sharejs:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lib.baomitu.com/social-share.js/1.0.16/js/social-share.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">sharejs_css:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lib.baomitu.com/social-share.js/1.0.16/css/share.min.css</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">gitalk:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/gitalk/1.7.2/gitalk.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">gitalk_css:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://lf6-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/gitalk/1.7.2/gitalk.min.css</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">valine:<